Terminal 2.2 compact powerful serial communication program. Scrollablecapture buffer. Continous capture to and send from TEXT file. Software orhardware handshake. XModem, YModem, ZModem, QuickB file transfer. AutomaticMacBinary format recognition, offline extraction, creation. Builtin Cinterpreter executes scripts from TEXT files (modem-setup auto-logon BBS).Text string macros. Program is free. C source available.